This is a program that analyzes the sentiment of a given text. It reads the text from an input file and identifies individual sentences. 
Using the files containing lists of positive and negative words, this program categorizes each sentence as either "Positive", "Negative", or 
"Neutral" based on the words it contains. The final output, consisting of each sentence and its corresponding sentiment label, is be written 
to a separate output file which is included in this folder. 
